english.title: come closer
text: Where was All these things from your meeting
Darling I hope I’ll stay with you like this
the most beautiful days were the days of our love
Arrab ya habibi = come closer darling
albi binadek = my heart is calling you
from this night i belong to you
who in this world ? except me?
tell me what can I do for this yearning
my heart melt with tow words
me and you will live most beautiful years
